data.description: Newly updated 5 bedroom, 2 bath farmhouse sitting on 10.95 private acres just a short distance outside of Oregon City.  This property offers unlimited options and incredible potential with several outbuildings including a 4 stall horse barn, a 24' X 24' shop with concrete floor, and a HUGE 40'X 84'X 16' sidewall warehouse with a gravel floor that has never been used since being built. All the outbuildings have power. Also included is a small animal shelter with power, and a potting shed. The house has all new fiber cement siding, and all new windows. Fresh paint on the exterior, and interior. New front door, and new rear glass slider. Both bathrooms have been fully updated. The primary bedroom is on the main floor and boasts a bathroom with overhead rainspout and wall jets in the shower, walk in closet, and glass slider to the back patio. New LVP flooring on the main level, and newer carpet upstairs. Updated electrical throughout. New customizable glass front refrigerator and stainless steel dishwasher are included, as well as the washer/dryer. John Deere riding lawnmower included. OPEN HOUSE SATURDAY OCTOBER 7th from 11:00 am to 1:00 PM.
